{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/h1.png?t=1738159018\" />Trapped in a room of the Italian genial inventor, you need to think out of the box to solve logical enigmas written in a book and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the answers, unlock the Cryptex, and see what awaits you in the next room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/1.gif?t=1738159018\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/h3.png?t=1738159018\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Da Vinci Cryptex</strong> is a brainteasing game consisting of 50 unique riddles, the more you go on, the harder to solve the puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, how many enigmas can you crack? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/2.png?t=1738159018\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Warning: this IQ game may be addictive!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666270/extras/h2.png?t=1738159018\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u00a050 unique handcrafted puzzles </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hints available (click the bulb button to get a hint) </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Astonishing graphics\u2211</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Captivating background music</strong> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_ta